00:17:08.558 --> 00:17:09.349
GRETCHEN RUBIN: No.

00:17:09.349 --> 00:17:11.460
I think a lot of authors of
things about productivity

00:17:11.460 --> 00:17:12.044
and efficiency.

00:17:12.044 --> 00:17:12.730
LOGAN URY: Yeah.

00:17:12.730 --> 00:17:13.050
GRETCHEN RUBIN:
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:17:13.050 --> 00:17:13.680
LOGAN URY: That
