00:17:13.680 --> 00:17:14.109
GRETCHEN RUBIN: I don't
know if anybody here

00:17:14.109 --> 00:17:15.490
has read Laura Vanderkam?

00:17:15.490 --> 00:17:17.300
She's a time management expert.

00:17:17.300 --> 00:17:18.790
I really love her stuff.

00:17:18.790 --> 00:17:24.760
And she was telling me
