00:17:29.870 --> 00:17:30.823
in the parking lot.

00:17:30.823 --> 00:17:32.610
[LAUGHTER]

00:17:33.287 --> 00:17:34.370
Because she's an upholder.

00:17:34.370 --> 00:17:39.220
But I think one of the
things is regular work.

00:17:39.220 --> 00:17:42.110
That's what works for me is to
work a little bit every day.

00:17:42.110 --> 00:17:50.290
And to really always
stay inside a project.

00:17:50.290 --> 00:17:51.020
I have a friend.

00:17:51.020 --> 00:17:52.677
She's a writer, he's a painter.

00:17:52.677 --> 00:17:54.260
And she said they
have this rule like,

00:17:54.260 --> 00:17:55.550
could you work for 10 minutes?

00:17:55.550 --> 00:17:57.540
Meaning are you
