00:27:13.090 --> 00:27:15.200
a certain kind of thing.

00:27:15.200 --> 00:27:18.254
Like I'm not going to see any--

00:27:18.254 --> 00:27:19.295
AUDIENCE: Baskin-Robbins?

00:27:19.295 --> 00:27:20.075
GRETCHEN RUBIN: Yeah.

00:27:20.075 --> 00:27:20.616
There you go!

00:27:20.616 --> 00:27:21.420
[LAUGHTER]

00:27:21.420 --> 00:27:21.920
Yeah.

00:27:21.920 --> 00:27:22.680
Somebody's speaking
from experience.

00:27:22.680 --> 00:27:23.586
Right.

