00:44:31.260 --> 00:44:33.430
But that I think is
my upholder nature.

00:44:33.430 --> 00:44:37.170
So I internalize the
checklist and it's not hard

00:44:37.170 --> 00:44:38.700
for me to do that.

00:44:38.700 --> 00:44:41.470
But I think for many people,
keeping the checklist probably

00:44:41.470 --> 00:44:44.040
might be useful indefinitely.

00:44:44.040 --> 00:44:47.920
Because it is a form
of self accountability.

00:44:47.920 --> 00:44:49.794
And so I don't.

00:44:49.794 --> 00:44:50.710
I don't have to do it.

00:44:50.710 --> 00:44:52.020
Well, I do some things.

00:44:52.020 --> 00:44:55.140
Like I keep a food diary.

00:44:55.140 --> 00:44:57.740
And for a while, I
was tracking my sleep,

00:44:57.740 --> 00:45:00.770
though I stopped doing that.

00:45:00.770 --> 00:45:03.910
But I think for a lot
of people, tracking

00:45:03.910 --> 00:45:06.230
is very useful for a long time.

00:45:06.230 --> 00:45:08.670
And it also gives you that
sense of accomplishment too.

00:45:08.670 --> 00:45:10.040
It's very satisfying.

00:45:10.040 --> 00:45:12.550
And it also keeps you from
feeling like you've blown it.

00:45:12.550 --> 00:45:14.530
Because you're like,
well, maybe I was bad.

00:45:14.530 --> 00:45:16.155
For three days, I
didn't keep my habit.

00:45:16.155 --> 00:45:17.890
But look, I did for so long.

00:45:17.890 --> 00:45:18.964
I can get back into that.

00:45:18.964 --> 00:45:20.380
So there's a lot
about it that can

00:45:20.380 --> 00:45:21.742
be reassuring and energizing.

00:45:21.742 --> 00:45:23.450
So I think for a lot
of people, it really

00:45:23.450 --> 00:45:26.920
is helpful to keep the
checklist going just depending

00:45:26.920 --> 00:45:28.415
on what works for you.

00:45:28.415 --> 00:45:29.600
AUDIENCE: Hi.

