00:48:20.980 --> 00:48:22.070
I got all these vitamins.

00:48:22.070 --> 00:48:23.456
The doctor told me to take them.

00:48:23.456 --> 00:48:24.430
I don't take them.

00:48:24.430 --> 00:48:27.280
And I said, well, do you
think you need to take them?

00:48:27.280 --> 00:48:28.927
She said no.

00:48:28.927 --> 00:48:31.510
If you thought that they really
mattered, you would take them.

00:48:31.510 --> 00:48:34.390
So I mean, a part of it is
just figuring out yourself

00:48:34.390 --> 00:48:36.754
so that then you can shape
the habit in a way that's

00:48:36.754 --> 00:48:37.670
going to work for you.

00:48:37.670 --> 00:48:41.230
Because there's
all different kinds

00:48:41.230 --> 00:48:45.673
